 {"id":"jeffreysprompts.com-z16","title":"Implement composite search engine (search/engine.ts)","description":"**Details:**
- `searchPrompts(query, limit, source)` is the main search interface
- Orchestrates tokenizer → synonyms → BM25
- Returns SearchResult[] with id, title, description, score, highlights

**SearchResult Type:**
```typescript
export interface SearchResult {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  description: string;
  content: string;
  score: number;
  highlights?: {
    title?: string[];
    description?: string[];
    content?: string[];
  };
}
```

**Implementation:**
```typescript
export function searchPrompts(
  query: string, 
  limit: number = 20,
  source: Prompt[] = prompts
): SearchResult[] {
  if (!query.trim()) return [];

  const tokens = tokenize(query);
  const expanded = expandWithSynonyms(tokens);
  const results = bm25Search(expanded, source);

  return results.slice(0, limit).map(r => ({
    id: r.prompt.id,
    title: r.prompt.title,
    description: r.prompt.description,
    content: r.prompt.content,
    score: r.score,
  }));
}
```

**Used By:** CLI search/suggest, Web SpotlightSearch, API routes

**Reasoning:** Single entry point for all search operations. Encapsulates tokenization, synonym expansion, and BM25 scoring.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-10T00:32:52.681142521-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-10T01:18:07.445622749-05:00","closed_at":"2026-01-10T01:18:07.445622749-05:00","close_reason":"Core package fully implemented with types, registry, bundles, workflows, schema, search (tokenize, synonyms, BM25, engine), export (skills, markdown, json), and template (render, variables)","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"jeffreysprompts.com-z16","depends_on_id":"jeffreysprompts.com-m5k","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-10T00:36:39.237126873-05:00","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
